{{!-- 
TASK MANAGEMENT TEMPLATE
========================

Purpose: Create Obsidian notes for tasks, projects, or work items with status tracking.

Required Fields:
- Task/Title: Name of the task
- Status: Current state (e.g., "Not Started", "In Progress", "Done")

Optional Fields:
- Priority: Importance level
- DueDate: Deadline
- Assignee: Person responsible
- Project: Parent project
- Notes: Additional context
- Subtasks: List of sub-items
- Tags: Categorical labels

Customization:
- Adjust frontmatter fields based on your data
- Modify status/priority values to match your workflow
- Add custom sections as needed
- Change tag format to match your system

Usage:
1. Replace {{FieldName}} with your actual CSV/JSON field names
2. Remove sections for fields you don't have
3. Add conditional logic for optional fields
4. Ensure YAML safety (quote strings with special chars)
--}}
---
{{!-- Core Metadata --}}
title: '{{Task}}'
type: task

{{!-- Status Tracking --}}
status: '{{Status}}'
{{#if Priority}}
priority: '{{Priority}}'
{{/if}}

{{!-- Dates --}}
{{#if DueDate}}
due: '{{DueDate}}'
{{/if}}
{{#if CreatedDate}}
created: '{{CreatedDate}}'
{{/if}}

{{!-- Relationships --}}
{{#if Assignee}}
assigned: '[[{{Assignee}}]]'
{{/if}}
{{#if Project}}
project: '[[{{Project}}]]'
{{/if}}

{{!-- Tags for Filtering --}}
tags: [task{{#if Status}}, status/{{Status}}{{/if}}{{#if Priority}}, priority/{{Priority}}{{/if}}{{#if Project}}, project/{{Project}}{{/if}}]

{{!-- Optional URL --}}
{{#if URL}}
source: '{{URL}}'
{{/if}}
---

# {{Task}}

{{!-- Status Badge --}}
**Status:** {{Status}}{{#if Priority}} | **Priority:** {{Priority}}{{/if}}{{#if DueDate}} | **Due:** {{DueDate}}{{/if}}

{{!-- Assignment --}}
{{#if Assignee}}
**Assigned to:** [[{{Assignee}}]]
{{/if}}

{{!-- Project Context --}}
{{#if Project}}
**Project:** [[{{Project}}]]
{{/if}}

{{!-- External Link --}}
{{#if URL}}
**Source:** [View in System]({{URL}})
{{/if}}

---

{{!-- Main Content --}}
{{#if Description}}
## Description

{{Description}}
{{/if}}

{{!-- Subtasks Section --}}
{{#if Subtasks}}
## Subtasks

{{#each Subtasks}}
- [ ] {{this}}
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{!-- Additional Notes --}}
{{#if Notes}}
## Notes

{{Notes}}
{{/if}}

{{!-- Dependencies Section --}}
{{#if BlockedBy}}
## Dependencies

**Blocked by:**
{{#each BlockedBy}}
- [[{{this}}]]
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

{{#if Blocks}}
**Blocking:**
{{#each Blocks}}
- [[{{this}}]]
{{/each}}
{{/if}}

---

## Activity Log

[Track work and updates here]

## Related Tasks

[Link related tasks and notes]